{"tid":2154891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾主理選舉爭議 政制局副秘羅淑佩掌運輸署","createTime":"2020-08-13T11:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T12:10:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fc613cc081188ccf166db4419a0a2842748566b1","tid":2154891,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/NXQISBVYXBDQZKCRFWQLKRU2VY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FNXQISBVYXBDQZKCRFWQLKRU2VY%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjziNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=2838e25c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FNXQISBVYXBDQZKCRFWQLKRU2VY%2F&h=820e0dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/NXQISBVYXBDQZKCRFWQLKRU2VY/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府今日公佈3個高層官員任命，政制及內地事務局副秘書長羅淑佩將於下月9日接任運輸署署長；公務員事務局副秘書長盧世雄則於本月24日出任工業貿易署長；而稅務局副局長譚大鵬則「升正」為局長，接替將退休的現任局長黃權輝。翻查資料，羅淑佩任政制局副秘期間曾去信法院，阻止記者查閱選民名冊。"},{"pid":"739fa6b54f11d662be3ce76dd87be2ea0431ea31","tid":2154891,"uid":343663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"又一件嫁唔出中女豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781932e6c75d6224fa51316b438a2cceaef8539e","tid":2154891,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d70904b3e8588bc6975d3a0331962dbce61ef000","tid":2154891,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781932e6c75d6224fa51316b438a2cceaef8539e","tid":2154891,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"佢似會建議肥人比一人錢可以坐兩個位/肥人可坐關愛座多d"},{"pid":"967dab4ab1dfa61d25cdce442320fbc2ff66a27c","tid":2154891,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:48:48.00